        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Gold Star Spouses Act of 20</b><strong>21</strong></p> <p>This bill provides interim appropriations for the Coast Guard Retired Serviceman's Family Protection and Survivor Benefits Plans if a bill providing appropriations for the plans has not been enacted before the fiscal year begins. </p> <p>The bill provides the appropriations at the rate of operations and under the terms and conditions provided by the most recent law making full-year appropriations for the plans.</p> <p>The appropriations provided by this bill are not available after a bill is enacted that (1) provides appropriations for the plans, or (2) provides appropriations for the Coast Guard without funding the plans.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
